Studio Ghibli style illustration of a solitary figure seated in peaceful meditation within a lush monastery garden in Singapore, surrounded by gentle concentric rings of soft golden light emanating outward in all directions. The warm glow extends beyond the figure, encompassing delicate tropical plants, small birds perched on branches, a curious cat nearby, and distant silhouettes of diverse people going about their lives. The light reaches upward into a twilight sky with soft clouds and downward where roots and earth creatures are subtly visible. The entire scene radiates warmth and compassion, with the ethereal golden waves connecting all living beings in a tender embrace. Soft watercolor textures, warm amber and sage green palette, dreamy atmospheric perspective.
